title: #92Noon! Friday Football Feast! Oake/Michaels/Greenway/Krantz/Gorg
description: Charch and Nordo are in for the Friday Football Feast. Brian Oake talks music returning amid the hopeful end of the pandemic, Bill Michaels talks Aaron Rodgers and the Packers dilemma, Chad Greenway makes his regular appearance, Nat Krantz joins the music conversation, and Kevin Gorg talks Wild and the Tom Wilson drama.
